"replyTime":"2020-06-17T14:11:00.000Z","msg":"天啟四騎士係咪到咗？"},{"pid":"12d7bacaeeb7964b4533443051ab135d619622fe","tid":2068241,"uid":306914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T14:11:29.000Z","msg":"yeah<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />蝗蟲滅蝗！"},{"pid":"a133c8939550caafd6fb3a32222f8d93b0dc08f3","tid":2068241,"uid":26770,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T14:11:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200611/PESG3Y64GFGWBRF2LAI6F3MFKU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200611%2FPESG3Y64GFGWBRF2LAI6F3MFKU%2F&d=u0uYB5UElWTGJsHKTdw4wWhNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=606174a9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200611%2FPESG3Y64GFGWBRF2LAI6F3MFKU%2F&h=3716bfe7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200611/PESG3Y64GFGWBRF2LAI6F3MFKU/</a><br />\n<br />\n【蝗蟲大軍】吉林、湖南、黑龍江現災情 專家估<ins>7月或爆發式增長</ins><br />\n<br />\n現在吉林、黑龍江、湖南等多個縣市又爆發「蝗災」，部份地區蝗蟲泛濫。目前雖還處於幼蟲階段，但蔓延速度很快，密度很大。<br />\n<br />\n哈爾濱市周邊和鄰近俄國的佳木斯市，分別爆發嚴重程度不一的蝗災，受災面積已達24,631畝。<br />\n<br />\n吉林市農業農村局也發佈緊急通知，表示在蛟河市、樺甸市、永吉縣、等縣轄市，均發生蟲害，截至4日，蝗蟲已襲近13.4公頃土地，密度最高可在每平方米發現50隻蝗蟲。"},{"pid":"17e9b9851b18016588353d648c6f2e4ea05a6ef6","tid":2068241,"uid":133319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3e07a170d7dcdf560702dd9811b06c822e08045","tid":2068241,"uid":266373,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T14:07:57.000Z","msg":"鬥蝗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T14:15:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25268ee981fc9e7f572188a9d245da59c0b0aace","tid":2068241,"uid":214173,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"rep